rows.description: All 803 GTEx v3 muscle samples combined by summing raw coverage values across all samples and also summing normalized splice-junction-spanning read counts across all samples. The normalization is done by computing the normalized read count for each junction as normalized_read_count = raw_read_count * scalar. Here scalar = average_unique_reads_per_muscle_sample / (total_unqiue_reads_in_this_sample * number_of_muscle_samples), and average_unique_reads_per_muscle_sample = (total_unqiue_reads_in_all_muscle_samples / number_of_muscle_samples)
rows.name: GTEx All Muscle - Norm.

rows.description: All 755 GTEx v3 blood samples combined by summing raw coverage values across all samples and also summing normalized splice-junction-spanning read counts across all samples. The normalization is done by computing the normalized read count for each junction as normalized_read_count = raw_read_count * scalar. Here scalar = average_unique_reads_per_blood_sample / (total_unqiue_reads_in_this_sample * number_of_blood_samples), and average_unique_reads_per_blood_sample = (total_unqiue_reads_in_all_blood_samples / number_of_blood_samples)
